graph LR
    Original[A·x = b] --> Precondition[Apply M⁻¹]
    Precondition --> Modified[M⁻¹·A·x = M⁻¹·b]
    Modified --> Solve[Solve with Krylov method]
    Solve --> Faster[Faster convergence]
    
    subgraph "Preconditioner Types"
        JacobiP[Jacobi<br/>M = diagA]
        DILU_P[DILU<br/>M = LDU where L,U ≈ A]
        GAMG_P[GAMG<br/>Multilevel]
    end
    
    Precondition --> JacobiP
    Precondition --> DILU_P
    Precondition --> GAMG_P